Description:
MineSweeping game implemented by Flex.

Run:
Make sure the mongodb server is running.
Make sure you have a running server that supports php.
Download the minesweeping folder and use your browser to navigate to
YOUR_DIR/minesweeping/bin-release/MineSweeping.html 

The source can be view by right-click the application and select "View Source" in the flash player menu. 

The database being used is "msdb" on localhost.
And the data is stored in collection called "state".
(Details can be found in YOUR_DIR/minesweeping/bin-release/php/dbRead.php & dbSave.php)
You can check this out after you've saved the game at least once.
>use msdb
>db.state.find()


